_description: A Book Plate — six lines in couplets

CamTCC597.Transcription:
Ho so on me doth lokeI am [ ] bokeShe prays you for hyr
                    sakenot me to withdrow nor takeWhen ye haue rede your fylldelyuer
                    me a gane with good wyll
CamTCC597.Note: Added to end flyleaf; name erased by subsequent owner.
